<dashboard version="1.1" theme="dark">
  <label>T1570 — Lateral Tool Transfer</label>
  <description>Lateral Tool Transfer (T1570). See cases/t1570_lateral_tool_transfer/README.md for the full triage runbook.</description>

  <fieldset submitButton="false" autoRun="true">
    <input type="time" token="time">
      <label>Time range</label>
      <default>
        <earliest>-24h@h</earliest>
        <latest>now</latest>
      </default>
    </input>
    <input type="text" token="src_filter" searchWhenChanged="true">
      <label>Source IP</label>
      <default>*</default>
    </input>
  </fieldset>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>Active alerts</title>
      <single>
        <search>
          <query>`lateral_tool_transfer`
| where like(src, "$src_filter$") OR "$src_filter$"="*"
| stats count</query>
          <earliest>$time.earliest$</earliest>
          <latest>$time.latest$</latest>
        </search>
        <option name="colorBy">value</option>
        <option name="rangeValues">[0,1,5]</option>
        <option name="rangeColors">["0x53a051","0xf8be34","0xdc4e41"]</option>
        <option name="useColors">1</option>
      </single>
    </panel>
    <panel>
      <title>Distinct sources</title>
      <single>
        <search>
          <query>`lateral_tool_transfer`
| where like(src, "$src_filter$") OR "$src_filter$"="*"
| stats dc(src)</query>
          <earliest>$time.earliest$</earliest>
          <latest>$time.latest$</latest>
        </search>
      </single>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>Alerts</title>
      <table>
        <search>
          <query>`lateral_tool_transfer`
| where like(src, "$src_filter$") OR "$src_filter$"="*"
| eval window=strftime(_time, "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M")
| sort -_time</query>
          <earliest>$time.earliest$</earliest>
          <latest>$time.latest$</latest>
        </search>
        <option name="count">25</option>
      </table>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>Underlying activity, top sources</title>
      <chart>
        <search>
          <query>index=zeek sourcetype=zeek:conn
| where orig_bytes >= 1000000
| timechart span=15m sum(orig_bytes) BY src limit=8</query>
          <earliest>$time.earliest$</earliest>
          <latest>$time.latest$</latest>
        </search>
        <option name="charting.chart">column</option>
        <option name="charting.chart.stackMode">stacked</option>
      </chart>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>About this detection</title>
      <html>
        <h3>T1570 — Lateral Tool Transfer</h3>
        <p>Copies the operator's toolkit between compromised hosts. Internal east-west large-uplink transfers are unusual — legitimate east-west bulk usually flows file-server → user, not user → user.</p>
        <p>Per Zeek conn.log record between two RFC-1918 hosts where orig_bytes >= 5 MB. Flag any such record. The per-record style (no aggregation) keeps the rule cheap.</p>
        <p>
          Tuning + false-positive notes:
          <a href="https://github.com/JacobRHess/detlab/blob/main/cases/t1570_lateral_tool_transfer/README.md" target="_blank">cases/t1570_lateral_tool_transfer/README.md</a>
        </p>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>
